data.description: This spectacular ranch is beautifully maintained throughout!  The updated, spacious, eat in kitchen includes all appliances, recessed lighting, and wood cabinetry with under lighting.  The open great room is bright and neutral leading to two first floor bedrooms, a full bath, and a laundry room.  The master bedroom has a full master bathroom.  A completely finished lower level provides a large space to relax or entertain and features a half bathroom, walk in closet, and large storage area.  Outside you will find a covered front porch, fully fenced backyard with patio, shed, two car attached garage, and manicured landscaping.   This home is a must see!
